<fieldset class="m-form-row">
<label class="a-label" for="FirstName"><label for="PrincipalPolicyHolder_FirstName">First name</label></label>
<div class="m-form-row__content">
<div class="m-show-more" data-contract="Less info" data-expand="More info" data-module="m-show-more">
<div>
<span class="expandoText">
<p>To make sure you get our best deal, please enter your name exactly as it appears on your driving licence. By entering your details here you take the role of   <em><u><span style="color: #004FB6"> Principal Policyholder (PPH)</span></u></em></p>
<span class="expandedText">
<p>If purchased, the policy will be your ultimate financial and administrative responsibility.</p><p>The PPH enters a contract on behalf of all drivers who insure their vehicles on the policy and therefore is the only person who can:</p><ul><li>Cancel the entire policy</li><li>Add or remove vehicles</li><li>Change the postal address</li></ul><p>The PPH cannot be changed, although any main driver can change or remove their vehicle or change their cover.</p>
</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
